      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-xl">How to uninstall the extension</h2>

      <div class="leading-relaxed text-base">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mt-4 mb-2">In Chrome</h3>
        <p>
          Open your extensions page by typing or pasting
          <code class="bg-neutral-600 text-white px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">chrome://extensions</code>
          into the address bar, then find “Open Access Button” and click <strong><em>Remove</em></strong>.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mt-6 mb-2">In Firefox</h3>
        <p>
          Open your add-ons page by typing or pasting
          <code class="bg-neutral-600 text-white px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">about:addons</code>
          into the address bar, find “Open Access Button”, click the three dots, and select <strong><em>Remove</em></strong>.
        </p>
